subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament
Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Tajuan Porter was the most outstanding player in the Pacific-10 Conference tournament, with 61 points in three games, and scored 14 in the Ducks’ 75-61 victory over Winthrop last Sunday.
